iiv.data

Interface CoordinateMap

  • All Superinterfaces:
    iiVScriptable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AffineCoordinateMap, LinearCoordinateMap, NiftiQFormCoordinateMap, NiftiSFormCoordinateMap

    public interface CoordinateMap
extends iiVScriptable
    Interface that describes routines for converting locations into Talairach space and some handy Talairach constants.
    Since:
    iiV1.0
    See Also:
    LinearCoordinateMap
